<bibRefCitation id="19C7089D6F990B96B283214F36F990F9" pageId="30" pageNumber="109">Rayment (1951)</bibRefCitation>
as Toowoomba and Mackay does not fit the distribution as we know it. Since Rayment did not examine the type of 
<taxonomicName id="35D1A2AB5A16530F1E102CC21808E4BF" lsidName="alpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="109" rank="species" species="alpha">alpha</taxonomicName>
, the basis of his statement about the distribution is unclear.
</paragraph>
